      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a reliable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts through gears, though it may not have the crispness of a newer model. The exterior and interior show typical signs of wear and tear consistent with its age, including some minor cosmetic blemishes and upholstery wear. It has been maintained sufficiently to keep it roadworthy, making it a solid, honest option for practical transportation.",
