    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It drives smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left for its next owner! If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
