      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 BMW 540i xDrive in a stunning Bluestone Metallic finish. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, and I have taken great care to maintain its performance and aesthetic. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper from city parking. The 19-inch alloy wheels are in great shape with only one wheel showing light curb rash. Inside, the Black Dakota leather is clean and free of tears; the cabin still carries that premium BMW scent, though you will notice some light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster from entry and exit. All electronics, from the iDrive navigation system to the heated seats and sun-roof, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has a full-service history, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed just 500 miles ago. The tires have approximately 60% tread life remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a solid, honest car that delivers a smooth, powerful ride every time.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, an exemplar of sustained performance and engineering excellence. Having undergone a rigorous inspection process, this automobile demonstrates a level of mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement that distinguishes it within its class. The interior and exterior maintain a sophisticated presence, reflecting the attentive care of its previous ownership. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver who demands a harmonious balance of reliability, luxury, and authoritative road presence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of being well-loved, but it runs like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcements to mitigate common structural fatigue, ensuring the integrity of the multi-link rear suspension and limited-slip differential under load. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. While the finish shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization of the Getrag 6-speed manual and the responsiveness of the steering rack remain sharp. This is a technically sound machine tuned for the purist who demands mechanical transparency and balanced handling dynamics.",
